  "body": {
    "export_view": {
      "value": "<h2 id=\"Qpop\u2122CompanionResources(withVideo)-WhatisQpopCompanion?\">What is Qpop Companion?</h2><p>Qpop is a customer-facing application designed to enhance interaction and engagement at the point of sale through a dedicated touchscreen device (tablet). Always facing the customer, Qpop allows for seamless interaction during the sales process by: Always facing the customer, Qpop allows for seamless interaction during the sales process by:</p><ul><li><p>Displaying in-store advertisements and promotions</p></li><li><p>Showing real-time ticket details for customer review</p></li><li><p>Presenting electronic forms and waivers for acknowledgment</p></li><li><p>Capturing electronic signatures for payments via integrated devices</p></li></ul><p>As a browser-based solution, Qpop eliminates the need for expensive proprietary hardware. Simply choose your preferred tablet or touchscreen device, pair it with your location, and start engaging with your customers!</p><a class=\"external-link\" data-card-appearance=\"embed\" data-layout=\"center\" data-original-height=\"480.00\" data-original-width=\"853.34\" data-width=\"100.00\" href=\"https://youtu.be/3kRhJkge87I\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://youtu.be/3kRhJkge87I</a><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" src=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/1937047567/Control%20-%20f79824.png?api=v2\"></span><h2 id=\"Qpop\u2122CompanionResources(withVideo)-GettingStarted\">Getting Started</h2><p><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://www.servicecentral.com/products/repair-q/hardware-recommendations/\" rel=\"nofollow\">RepairQ Hardware Recommendations</a></p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1936523288/Qpop+Companion+System+Requirements\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1936523288\" data-linked-resource-version=\"8\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Qpop\u2122 Companion System Requirements</a></p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1936261206/Qpop+Companion+Recommended+Image+Resolutions\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1936261206\" data-linked-resource-version=\"7\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Qpop\u2122 Companion - Recommended Image Resolutions</a></p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1936588867/Qpop+Companion+-+Enable+Kiosk+Mode+on+iOS\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1936588867\" data-linked-resource-version=\"9\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Qpop\u2122 Companion - Enable Kiosk Mode on iOS</a></p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1936523314/Qpop+Companion+-+Enable+Kiosk+Mode+on+Android\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1936523314\" data-linked-resource-version=\"6\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Qpop\u2122 Companion - Enable Kiosk Mode on Android</a></p><h2 id=\"Qpop\u2122CompanionResources(withVideo)-QpopCompanionSetup\">Qpop Companion Setup</h2><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1937014846/Create+a+Qpop+Companion\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1937014846\" data-linked-resource-version=\"13\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Create a Qpop Companion</a> - Location Admin, Admin Roles</p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1936490516/Pair+a+Qpop+Companion\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1936490516\" data-linked-resource-version=\"10\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Pair a Qpop Companion</a> - Shift Lead, Manager, Admin Roles</p><h2 id=\"Qpop\u2122CompanionResources(withVideo)-QpopAdditionalFeatures\">Qpop Additional Features</h2><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1936949331/Send+Custom+Forms+to+Your+Qpop+Companion+Device\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1936949331\" data-linked-resource-version=\"8\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Send Custom Forms to Qpop Companion</a></p><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1936359503/Capture+Integrated+Payment+Signatures+on+a+Qpop+Companion\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1936359503\" data-linked-resource-version=\"6\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Enable Signature Capture for Integrated Payment Transactions</a></p><h2 id=\"Qpop\u2122CompanionResources(withVideo)-QpopTroubleshooting\">Qpop Troubleshooting</h2><p><a href=\"https://servicecentral.atlassian.net/wiki/spaces/SCD/pages/1936654410/Qpop+Companion+Troubleshooting\" data-linked-resource-id=\"1936654410\" data-linked-resource-version=\"8\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\">Qpop Companion Troubleshooting</a></p><p /><p /><p>START 1.21.X</p>",
